column2:
NEPA identifies which of the following big questions that must be addressed in an Environmental Impact Statements.
1. The purpose of the Environmental Impact Statement;
2. Environmental consequences of the proposed action;
3路 Alternatives to the proposed action;
4路 The relationship between local short-term uses of man's environment and the maintenance and enhancement of long-term productivity
A. 1, 2
B. 1, 2, 3
C. 1, 2, 4
D. 1, 2, 3, 4
